title: Investing In Your Future
itunes:title: Investing In Your Future
description:
When you stay focused on past hurts and disappointments, you invest in your past instead of your future. It’s time to let go of what happened in the past. Where you're headed is more important than where you've been. Release the pain of the past and trust that God has greater things ahead!Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love. To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
